Package com.google.cloud.bigquery

Class TableInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.cloud.bigquery.TableInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Table
    public class TableInfo
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Google BigQuery table information. Use StandardTableDefinition to create simple BigQuery table. Use ViewDefinition to create a BigQuery view. Use ExternalTableDefinition to create a BigQuery a table backed by external data.
    See Also:
    Managing Tables, Serialized Form
